                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Primary Stage (Ages 5-11)</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                    Cambridge Primary curriculum with core subjects and enhanced Islamic Studies program.
                </p>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                        <span class="icon-[tabler--check] text-green-500 size-4"></span>
